>> title: ❄️ Gazpacho
>> type: soup
>> time (minutes): 30
>> yield (servings): 4

Combine @tomato{4%large, chopped}, @cucumber{1%chopped}, @sweet onion{1/2%large, chopped}, @green bell pepper{1%seeded and diced}, @minced garlic{1%teaspoon}, @tomato juice{1%cup}, @red wine vinegar{2%tablespoons}, and @olive oil{3%tablespoons} in #food processor{} or #blender until liquefied.

Add @pepper, @hot sauce{} or @cayenne pepper{}, and @lemon juice{} to taste - mix well. 

Allow soup to chill thoroughly.